title: iShoot - March 2016
description:
English | 100 pages | PDF | 56.1 Mb




iShoot is dedicated to the live quarry shotgunner. Catering for all shooters, from driven game shots, to pigeon decoyers - including wildfowlers and those who like it rough and varied, plus regular gun reviews, it is an all-encompassing read with quality embedded video. A section on gamekeeping will be of interest to the amateur keeper and examples of sport found abroad will provide inspiration for all. This free digital magazine is the only in-depth publication of its kind dedicated to the UK shotgunner and is set to be a firm favourite with sporting shooters
